dct_title_s: Deutschland Politisch / bearbeitel von Dr. W. Eggers.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Panel title. Panel on verso includes charts showing information on the population of the Federal Republic of Germany from 1946 to 1954. "Best.- Nr. 76."
